	<li> <strong><a href="http://www.qualitymeasures.ahrq.gov/tutorial/index.aspx">Tutorials on Quality Measures</a>. </strong>National Quality Measures Clearinghouse, Agency for Healthcare Research and Quality.  These tutorials provide an introduction to the field of quality measurement and how best to use resources available from the National Quality Measures Clearinghouse. Topics include quality care measures related to health care delivery and to population health; desired attributes, uses, selection, and validity of clinical quality measures; and finding care-coordination measures.  Introductory level, print format, self-paced.  </li>
	
